Ghobdcalc (hexadecimal, Octal, Binary, Decimal calculator)
an multibase calculator with several functionnalities.

for installation simply type:

  $ ./configure          # This will perform a system check and set some variables.
  $ make                 # This will build the shared and the static library
  $ sudo make install    # This will install Ghobdcalc on your system.

for uninstall Ghobdcalc simply type:

  $ sudo make uninstall  # This will remove Ghobdcalc fully from your system.


